                 1 =|    O    |= 16
                   =|         |=
                   =|   MAX   |=
                   =|   232   |=   Top View
                   =|         |=
                   =|         |=
                   =|         |=
                 8 =|_________|= 9

    The connectors for the DB-50XG card are to bottom of the PCB.
    The pins of the doublerowed pinconnector that are not used, you must
    pull away. Then press the other pins down up to the surface of the
    plastic part, that holds all the pins. Put then from top to bottom
